# a list of JSON objects.
# Written by Joshua Root <jmr@macports.org>, 2017
# Requires: tclsh with the tcllib 'json' package.
#
# Usage:
#     tclsh portindex2json.tcl path/to/PortIndex [--info <key>=<value>]
#     tclsh portindex2json.tcl --help
